@clientEmail = client01@email.com
@clientPassword = 12345678
@profId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Login do CLIENT (define {{token}})
POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{clientEmail}}",
  "password": "{{clientPassword}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### Lista favoritos do cliente autenticado
GET {{base_url}}/api/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Favoritar profissional — 201 na 1ª vez, 200 quando já existe
POST {{base_url}}/api/favorites/{{profId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lista de novo — deve incluir o profissional acima
GET {{base_url}}/api/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Desfavoritar — 204 (idempotente)
DELETE {{base_url}}/api/favorites/{{profId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
